## Paired Model Architecture

This project uses the **paired model** architecture:

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/
├── assistant/          # Document generation assistant
│   ├── index.html      # Main UI
│   ├── js/             # Application logic
│   │   └── core/       # → symlink to assistant-core/src
│   ├── css/            # Styles
│   ├── tests/          # Unit tests
│   └── prompts/        # Phase prompts (if applicable)
├── validator/          # Document quality validator
│   ├── index.html      # Validator UI
│   ├── js/             # Scoring logic
│   │   └── core/       # → symlink to validator-core/src
│   ├── tests/          # Unit tests
│   └── testdata/       # Scoring fixtures
├── package.json        # Shared dependencies
└── jest.config.js      # Shared test config
```

**Core Libraries** (via symlinks):
- `assistant-core`: Shared UI components, storage, workflow logic
- `validator-core`: Shared validation infrastructure

