## Symlink Handling

**Local Development**: Symlinks work natively.

**CI/CD**: The CI workflow clones core repos and replaces symlinks:
```yaml
- name: Clone core repos
  run: |
    git clone https://github.com/bordenet/assistant-core.git
    git clone https://github.com/bordenet/validator-core.git
    rm -rf assistant/js/core validator/js/core
    cp -r assistant-core/src assistant/js/core
    cp -r validator-core/src validator/js/core
```

